Next, I asked for medium rare and it was perfect.
Charred outer crust but starting 1mm inside the burger was a perfectly even pink, soft consistency; perfect.
I've had many of the "best" burgers in the west and this is as good as anything else out there.
Yes, the burger is good enough to warrant 5 stars.
I've been craving this burger since the day after I had my second.
This is just a perfect, no frills medium rare burger.
Tip: get a double, it's only $3 more.
