He offered me a free mojito or a bloody mary - ok, I'm not going to drink and drive with my child THANKS but NO THANKS.
What a horrible experience that was.
I've always enjoyed the Mandalay Bay Hotel and Casino, but they really need to re-staff or re-train those people running that place they would like to call an establishment.

